  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BE A GIGACRAB !!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to be a true <strong>Gigacrab</strong>? Get ready to face the most epic (and absurd) challenge you've ever seen. Just you, your <strong>claws</strong>, and the path to glory (or <strong>despair</strong>).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/4c817246eaa80894f7121fb355535921.poster.avif?t=1758929115\" width=700 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/4c817246eaa80894f7121fb355535921.webm?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/4c817246eaa80894f7121fb355535921.mp4?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PREPARE YOUR CLAWS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show your strength and master the art of <strong>swinging</strong> toward success. The path will be full of obstacles and <strong>challenges</strong> that will test your <strong>patience</strong>, but a true <strong>Gigacrab</strong> always finds a way to overcome the impossible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/5e4ace8d8c225c68c3ac41d1b5c008ff.poster.avif?t=1758929115\" width=700 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/5e4ace8d8c225c68c3ac41d1b5c008ff.webm?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/5e4ace8d8c225c68c3ac41d1b5c008ff.mp4?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET UP AND KEEP CLIMBING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every <strong>failure</strong> is a <strong>lesson</strong>, and every fall makes you stronger. Being a true <strong>Gigacrab</strong> means embracing frustration, learning from it, and moving forward... even if it means <strong>falling</strong> again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/e13891d69c68b1000ca5299fdcf6bd86.poster.avif?t=1758929115\" width=700 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/e13891d69c68b1000ca5299fdcf6bd86.webm?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/e13891d69c68b1000ca5299fdcf6bd86.mp4?t=1758929115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445090/extras/32601c47df22b39926d0d4fdc8d805c4.avif?t=1758929115\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p>",
